profile_positions.description:
I provided internal & external communications for research groups focusing on vaccine R&D, immunology and disease prevention:
•	Created brochures and congress materials clearly positioning these groups and their innovative science;
•	Edited scientific manuscripts subsequently published in top journals;
•	Strengthened Janssen’s relationships with key stakeholders by telling the company’s story in website copy, blogs, video scripts, in-depth articles, and interviews with scientific leaders and collaborators;   
•	Produced newsletters sharing knowledge and promoting employee engagement;
•	Wrote effective Management Team communications and press releases;

In addition, I was Associate Editor & Chief Writer of an internal (digital and print) magazine about pharma R&D and healthcare innovation, for Johnson & Johnson employees worldwide (2015—2017).

JOURNALISM & PR: I wrote innumerable articles about travel, business, medical innovation, art, film and history for magazines such as 'Holland Herald' (KLM in-flight magazine), 'Holland Horizon' (Dutch Ministry of Foreign Affairs magazine), 'Het Financieele Dagblad' (Dutch financial daily), 'Orgyn' (Organon’s magazine of women's health).

TRANSLATION: Regular work for Radio Nederland Wereldomroep, the Netherlands’ world broadcasting service; 'Het Financieele Dagblad' and associated English-language weekly; Dutch National Advisory Council for Education (policy documents, annual report).

EDITING: Commissioning editor for 'Cityhopper Magazine' in the 'Holland Herald';  
English-language editor for 'Dox', international magazine on documentary film; 
Regular copy-editing of 'Helix' (biotechnology journal) and 'Orgyn' (women’s health magazine).
